<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="facility-n">facility <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fə'sɪləti/    美 /fə'sɪləti/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>设施；设备：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All rooms have <strong>private facilities</strong> (= a private bathroom).
所有房间都有独立的卫浴。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hotel has its own pool and <strong>leisure facilities</strong>.
这家酒店拥有自己的游泳池和休闲设施。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(用于某种活动、行业或服务的) 场所；建筑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a pet care facility 
宠物护理中心</p><footer>2013 江苏</footer></div></div>